---
import BaseHead from '../../../../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../../../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../../../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../../../../consts';
import FormattedDate from '../../../../components/FormattedDate.astro';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title="Thunder King Flame Event Guide - Zone Nova - GachaWiki" description="Complete guide for the Thunder King Flame event in Zone Nova" />
		<style>
			main {
				width: 960px;
				margin: 0 auto;
				padding: 2rem 1rem;
				line-height: 1.6;
			}
			
			.breadcrumb {
				margin-bottom: 2rem;
				color: rgb(var(--gray));
			}
			
			.breadcrumb a {
				color: #8B4513;
				text-decoration: none;
			}
			
			.breadcrumb a:hover {
				text-decoration: underline;
			}
			
			.event-guide {
				background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
				border: 2px solid #8B4513;
				border-radius: 12px;
				padding: 2rem;
				box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
			}
			
			.page-header {
				text-align: center;
				margin-bottom: 3rem;
			}
			
			.page-title {
				font-size: 2.5rem;
				color: #8B4513;
				margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
				border-bottom: 3px solid #8B4513;
				padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
			}
			
			.event-dates {
				font-size: 1.1rem;
				color: rgb(var(--gray));
				margin: 0 0 2rem 0;
				font-weight: bold;
			}
			
			.event-guide h2 {
				color: #8B4513;
				font-size: 1.8rem;
				margin: 2rem 0 1rem 0;
				border-left: 4px solid #8B4513;
				padding-left: 1rem;
			}
			
			.event-guide h3 {
				color: #8B4513;
				font-size: 1.4rem;
				margin: 1.5rem 0 0.8rem 0;
			}
			
			.event-section {
				background: #f8f6f0;
				border: 2px solid #8B4513;
				border-radius: 8px;
				padding: 1.5rem;
				margin: 2rem 0;
			}
			
			.mode-grid {
				display: grid;
				grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
				gap: 1rem;
				margin: 1rem 0;
			}
			
			.mode-card {
				background: white;
				border: 1px solid #8B4513;
				border-radius: 8px;
				padding: 1rem;
			}
			
			.mode-title {
				font-size: 1.2rem;
				font-weight: bold;
				color: #8B4513;
				margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
			}
			
			.shop-grid {
				display: grid;
				grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
				gap: 1rem;
				margin: 1rem 0;
			}
			
			.shop-image {
				width: 100%;
				border-radius: 4px;
				border: 1px solid #8B4513;
			}
			
			.bonus-section {
				background: #f0f8ff;
				border: 1px solid #8B4513;
				border-radius: 6px;
				padding: 1rem;
				margin: 1rem 0;
			}
			
			.tip-box {
				background: #fff3cd;
				border: 1px solid #ffc107;
				border-radius: 6px;
				padding: 1rem;
				margin: 1rem 0;
			}
			
			.tip-box h4 {
				color: #856404;
				margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
			}
			
			.tip-box ul {
				margin: 0;
				padding-left: 1rem;
				color: #856404;
			}
			
			.event-image {
				width: 100%;
				border-radius: 8px;
				margin: 1rem 0;
				border: 2px solid #8B4513;
			}
			
			strong {
				color: #8B4513;
			}
			
			hr {
				border: none;
				border-top: 2px solid #8B4513;
				margin: 2rem 0;
			}
			
			@media (max-width: 720px) {
				main {
					padding: 1rem;
				}
				
				.event-guide {
					padding: 1.5rem;
				}
				
				.page-title {
					font-size: 2rem;
				}
				
				.mode-grid,
				.shop-grid {
					grid-template-columns: 1fr;
				}
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<!-- Breadcrumb -->
			<nav class="breadcrumb">
				<a href="/blog/">Blog</a> → 
				<a href="/blog/zone-nova/">Zone Nova</a> → 
				<a href="/blog/zone-nova/events/">Events</a> → 
				Thunder King Flame
			</nav>

			<!-- Event Guide Content -->
			<article class="event-guide">
				<!-- Page Header -->
				<header class="page-header">
					<h1 class="page-title">⚡ Thunder King Flame Event (雷鸣王焰)</h1>
					<p class="event-dates">📅 Event Period: May 27, 2025 14:15 - June 10, 2025 03:59 (UTC+8)</p>
				</header>

				<img src="/images/event-kingflame/Eventkingflame.jpg" alt="Thunder King Flame Event" class="event-image" />

				<p>
					Experience the power of thunder and flame in this epic limited-time event! Battle through story stages, 
					tackle challenging modes, and collect exclusive rewards in the event shop.
				</p>

				<h2>📋 Event Structure</h2>
				<div class="event-section">
					<div class="mode-grid">
						<div class="mode-card">
							<div class="mode-title">📖 Story Mode (故事)</div>
							<p><strong>13 Stages Total</strong></p>
							<ul>
								<li>活动剧情 01-05: Initial stages</li>
								<li>活动剧情 06-09: Mid-tier stages</li>
								<li>活动剧情 10-13: Final stages</li>
							</ul>
							<p><strong>Note:</strong> Progressive unlock - complete stages in order</p>
						</div>
						
						<div class="mode-card">
							<div class="mode-title">⚔️ Challenge Mode (挑战)</div>
							<p><strong>3 Difficulty Levels</strong></p>
							<ul>
								<li>简单 (Easy) - ⭐</li>
								<li>正常 (Normal) - ⭐⭐</li>
								<li>困难 (Hard) - ⭐⭐⭐</li>
							</ul>
							<p>Higher difficulty levels offer better rewards</p>
						</div>
					</div>

					<h3>📊 Story Stage Rewards</h3>
					<ul>
						<li>First clear rewards for each stage</li>
						<li>Event currency for shop exchanges</li>
						<li>Various crafting materials</li>
						<li>Character experience and gold</li>
					</ul>
				</div>

				<hr>

				<h2>🛒 Event Shop</h2>
				<div class="event-section">
					<p>Use event currency to purchase exclusive items and materials:</p>
					
					<div class="shop-grid">
						<img src="/images/event-kingflame/EventShop1.jpg" alt="Event Shop Page 1" class="shop-image" />
						<img src="/images/event-kingflame/eventshop2.jpg" alt="Event Shop Page 2" class="shop-image" />
						<img src="/images/event-kingflame/eventshop3.jpg" alt="Event Shop Page 3" class="shop-image" />
					</div>
					
					<p style="font-weight: bold; color: #8B4513; margin-top: 1rem;">💡 General good buys available in the event shop!</p>

					<h3>🎯 Shop Priority Guide</h3>
					<ol>
						<li><strong>Limited Character Shards</strong> - Only available during this event</li>
						<li><strong>Rare Crafting Materials</strong> - Hard to obtain elsewhere</li>
						<li><strong>Rune Enhancement Items</strong> - Always valuable for progression</li>
						<li><strong>Premium Currencies</strong> - Good value for long-term planning</li>
						<li><strong>Common Materials</strong> - Buy if you have excess currency</li>
					</ol>
				</div>

				<hr>

				<h2>🎯 Activity Bonus System (活动加成效果)</h2>
				<div class="event-section">
					<img src="/images/event-kingflame/bounseevent.jpg" alt="Activity Bonus System" style="width: 100%; border-radius: 4px; margin: 0.5rem 0;" />
					
					<div class="bonus-section">
						<h3>🌟 Bonus Character System</h3>
						<p>Use specific characters to increase event currency gains:</p>
						
						<ul>
							<li><strong>主加乘角色 (Main Bonus Characters):</strong> Provide 20%-80% currency bonus</li>
							<li><strong>加成角色 (Additional Bonus Characters):</strong> Provide 10%-30% currency bonus</li>
							<li><strong>💡 Pro Tip:</strong> You don't need to use the characters in battle - just having them in your roster is enough!</li>
							<li><strong>⚡ Maximum Efficiency:</strong> Use a full team of bonus characters to maximize farming efficiency!</li>
						</ul>

						<h4>📈 Bonus Calculation</h4>
						<p>
							Bonuses from different characters stack additively. A team with multiple bonus characters 
							can significantly increase your farming efficiency, allowing you to clear the event shop faster.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</article>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html> 